OL,3,CWater company sending tankers to homes
OL,4,Cwithout sewers is 'scandal', says local
OL,6,FA north Cornwall pub landlord says
OL,7,F"scandal" is brewing in his village
OL,8,Fafter South West Water reportedly told
OL,9,Fa housing developer there was an
OL,10,Fadequate sewage disposal system to
OL,11,Fsupport more than 20 new homes.
OL,13,FRaw sewage is being pumped into
OL,14,Fwaiting lorries at St Mabyn, near
OL,15,FWadebridge, because a treatment works
OL,16,Fhas yet to be connected.
OL,18,FThe parish council claims that South
OL,19,FWest Water mistakenly thought a sewage
OL,20,Ftreatment works existed when it did
OL,21,Fnot.
