OL,3,CWater company sending tankers to homes
OL,4,Cwithout sewers is 'scandal', says local
OL,6,FRichard Ashton, landlord of the St
OL,7,FMabyn Inn, said: "It's been a bit of a
OL,8,Fscandal, really.
OL,10,F"They've let us know by letter in
OL,11,FJanuary that they're going to be
OL,12,Fproviding tankers to start draining
OL,13,Fthe sewage from the site, but we need
OL,14,Fto know what the permanent fix is for
OL,15,Fthis.
OL,17,F"I mean, they've disrupted the
OL,18,Fvillage. They've dug through and
OL,19,Fconnected to a treatment plant that
OL,20,Fwas only ever supporting ten houses.
