OL,6,F"So as a village, over the last two or
OL,7,Fthree years, we've reached out to
OL,8,FSouth West Water and explained, you
OL,9,Fknow, we have people in the city that
OL,10,Fhave been here all their life and as
OL,11,Fchildren will have seen this treatment
OL,12,Fplant fail.
OL,14,F"So we were telling them that it's not
OL,15,Fgoing to work, and yet it's still
OL,16,Fhappened. So as of yet, we've had
OL,17,Fnothing is to say what they're going
OL,18,Fto do, what they're going to provide
OL,19,Fother than the tankers are getting
OL,20,Fmore and more frequent."
