OL,3,CWater company sending tankers to homes
OL,4,Cwithout sewers is 'scandal', says local
OL,6,FLisa Pendlebury, who lives on the
OL,7,FChapelfields development totalling 27
OL,8,Fhouses, said that the sewage issue had
OL,9,Fnot impacted her life on the site.
OL,11,FShe said: "The sewage issue hasn't
OL,12,Fbeen a problem for us, we don't see a
OL,13,Fproblem, the water works, the toilets
OL,14,Fflush, the hot water works so we're
OL,15,Fnot seeing it from the inside.
OL,17,F"However, we were affected by the
OL,18,Fplans over the years because it caused
OL,19,Fquite a substantial delay in us
OL,20,Fgetting this house.
