OL,3,CWater company sending tankers to homes
OL,4,Cwithout sewers is 'scandal', says local
OL,6,FSpeaking to the Local Democracy
OL,7,FReporting Service, St Mabyn Parish
OL,8,FCouncil's chairman claimed that SWW
OL,9,Fhad ignored years of warnings from the
OL,10,Fcouncil and local residents that what
OL,11,Fit had described as a "sewage
OL,12,Ftreatment works" did not in fact,
OL,13,Fexist.
OL,15,FLast year, the company carried out
OL,16,Fpipe-laying in the village even though
OL,17,Fthere was nowhere for the sewage to go.
