OL,3,CWater company sending tankers to homes
OL,4,Cwithout sewers is 'scandal', says local
OL,6,FSouth West Water says it is now
OL,7,Fapplying to upgrade the local
OL,8,Fwastewater treatment works so it can
OL,9,Freceive new flows from the homes.
OL,11,FCarol Bray, a St Mabyn Parish Council
OL,12,Fmember and resident, said: "It's
OL,13,Fabsolutely dreadful. It's a dreadful
OL,14,Fmistake from the start.
OL,16,F"I on a personal level, wrote and
OL,17,Fexpressed my concern in February 2020,
OL,18,Ffive years ago about this because we
OL,19,Fhaven't got a main sewerage and nobody
OL,20,Ftook any notice.
