OL,3,CWater company sending tankers to homes
OL,4,Cwithout sewers is 'scandal', says local
OL,6,F"The main thing really is that it just
OL,7,Fcan't go on like this. They have got
OL,8,Fto make a better solution very, very
OL,9,Fsoon or else it's going to be
OL,10,Fdisaster. The more people move in, the
OL,11,Fmore the problem becomes."
OL,13,FSt Mabyn Parish Council is demanding
OL,14,Fthat South West Water should now come
OL,15,Fto the village for a meeting to
OL,16,Fexplain its long-term solution.
