OL,3,CWater company sending tankers to homes
OL,4,Cwithout sewers is 'scandal', says local
OL,6,FThe company told ITV News: "We
OL,7,Fcontinue to carry out daily checks on
OL,8,Fthe private pumping station and we are
OL,9,Fusing a tanker to remove flows until
OL,10,Four upgrade has been completed.
OL,12,F"We are applying to the Environment
OL,13,FAgency for a new permit which will
OL,14,Fallow us to progress with the upgrade
OL,15,Fto the local wastewater treatment
OL,16,Fworks so it can receive new flows from
OL,17,Fthe Chapelfields development."
